.container
  .mast-head
    %h1.mast-title Ready to team up?
    %h2.mast-sub-title Easily join or Create your League of Legends team.
    .summoner-enter

      = form_for @summoner, html: {class:'form-inline summoner-init'} do |f|
        = f.text_field :name, class:'summoner-name', placeholder:'Enter Summoner Name'
        .summoner-region-wrap
          = f.select :region, options_for_select([['NA', 'NA'], ['EUW', 'EUW']])
        :javascript
          $("#summoner_region").customSelect()

        = f.submit 'Enter', class:'btn btn-primary summoner-submit'

      .small-text
        By clicking enter you are agreeing to the
        %a{:href => "#terms"} terms
    -#.member-numbers 321,943 members and growing





.container
  .page-header{style:'text-transform:uppercase;'}
    %h2 Being apart of something bigger then yourself
  %p
    Whether you are into extremely competitive gaming or just casual game play with friends, its always better when there is team synergy. We feel like a large frustration in the game is wen teammates donâ€™t get along and game play starts to go from fun to frustrating. We have made assembling a team quick and easy. Team up with players who have similar gaming schedules (nights and weekends etc). Fill a specific role your team is missing. See actual game stats on a player before you whose to except them into team.
  %p
    Once a team is assembled keep track of all your team matches and collaborate on the game play strategies and critic each others plays. With match notes and living team chat you can keep a living record on each match.




.container.marketing
  .jumbotron
    / Three columns of text below the carousel
    .row
      .col-lg-4.large-icon
        %i.fa.fa-users
        %h3 Easy Team Building
        %p Our team building system takes the pain out of setting up a team. We automatically mach you with like players in your area with the skills to fill the desired roles for your team. No more scraping together a team.

      .col-lg-4.large-icon
        %i.fa.fa-headphones
        %h3 Skype Integration
        %p Conveniently launch a Skype conference call with all team members without having to know there Skype names. Just hit the group call button and everyone will be in the same call.

      .col-lg-4.large-icon
        %i.fa.fa-bar-chart-o
        %h3 Full Team history and Stats
        %p Full team analytics and team dynamic are charted out including gold per minute averages and and KDA ratios. You can also take team notes on a each match, vote on and MVP and upload your League Replay.


